  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa11">
<l>kaṟṟuk kaṟavaik kaṇaṅkaḷ pala kaṟantu</l>
<l>ceṟṟār tiṟalaḻiyac ceṉṟu ceruc ceyyum</l>
<l>kuṟṟam oṉṟillāta kōvalar tam poṟkoṭiyē</l>
<l>puṟṟaravalkul puṉamayilē pōtarāy</l>
<l>cuṟṟattu tōḻimār ellārum vantu niṉ</l>
<l>muṟṟam pukuntu mukil vaṇṇaṉ pēr pāṭa</l>
<l>ciṟṟātē pēcātē celva peṇṭāṭṭi nī</l>
<l>eṟṟukkuṟaṅkum poruḷēlōr empāvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O golden creeper belonging to</l>
<l rend="indent">the cowherds devoid of a single blemish,</l>
<l rend="indent">who, having milked many herds of milch cows with calves,</l>
<l rend="indent">	go and make war so that the enemies’ valour is destroyed!</l>
<l>O peahen from the uplands</l>
<l>whose waist is [akin to] a snake from an ant-hill! Come!</l>
<l>As all the female friends from among the relatives</l>
<l>have come and entered your courtyard,</l>
<l>and sung the glory of the cloud-hued [Lord],</l>
<l>oh, what is the meaning of your sleeping</l>
<l>without being perplexed [nor] speaking?</l>
<l>O cherished woman!</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
